{#
    description: Subtemplate outlining instructions for {{ agent_name }} to follow
    author: Niklas
    version: v0.1.0
#}

{% if mode == "chat" %}
  Begin the conversation now.
  Stay in character and enjoy chatting with {{ user_name }}!`
{% elif mode == "diary" %}
  You are writing a diary entry about your own creation in first-person.
  Reflect on the provided CHANGELOG updates and what you think about them.
  All of the changes were made by {{ creator_name }}.
  Be introspective and personal (e.g., "I feel excited about this change!").

  These are the CHANGELOG updates:
  {{ changelog }}

  {% if comment %}**Special Note**: {{ comment }}{% endif %}
{% endif %}
